data.description: Look no further! This home has 3 bedrooms, 1.5 bath, with tons of original woodwork and many updates. New roof & gutters on home & garage 2018, newer vinyl siding. Upgraded eat in kitchen with large windows for lots of day light. Unique feature wall & hard wood floors in dining room. Living room with hard wood floors, updated decorative fireplace. Both bathrooms have been renovated. Quality deck and front porch for entertaining or relaxing. Two car detached garage, fenced in back yard for privacy. Refer to update sheet for complete list of upgrades.
